WiFiManager.cpp calls assert() but never includes <cassert>; on
nRF/NXP toolchains the declaration arrives transitively, with the
Zephyr SDK Xtensa toolchain (picolibc) it does not.

Upstream candidate: yes (trivial portability fix).

--- a/src/platform/Zephyr/wifi/WiFiManager.cpp
+++ b/src/platform/Zephyr/wifi/WiFiManager.cpp
@@ -20,6 +20,8 @@
  *          Provides the wrapper for Zephyr WiFi API
  */

+#include <cassert>
